    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six engineering. Benefiting from a meticulously maintained VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, the chassis remains rigid and responsive. The naturally aspirated 3.2L powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential. Finished in factory-spec paint with pristine bushings and original suspension geometry, this vehicle operates at peak factory tolerances. It is a true turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
