    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases or wear, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, operates with precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
