      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and the interior is absolutely flawless. It drives like a dream and still has that new car smell! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been treated with absolute love, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
